{"_id": "rt_bg001", "name": "RT Background: Rogue Trader Dynasty", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Charm, Command, Common Lore (Rogue Traders), Linguistics (any), Scholastic Lore (Astromancy)\n\nStarting Talents: Air of Authority, Peer (Nobility)\n\nStarting Equipment: Best-quality sword or pistol, fine clothing worth 500 thrones, dynasty signet ring, personal vox, servo-skull\n\nBackground Bonus: Dynasty Legacy: +10 to all Commerce and Inquiry tests related to trade. Access to Dynasty resources once per session (value up to Profit Factor).\n\nAptitudes: Fellowship or Leadership\n\nBackground: As if anyone from a dynasty could have a single homeworld...", "benefit": "Aptitudes: Fellowship or Leadership | Dynasty Legacy: +10 to all Commerce and Inquiry tests related to trade. Access to Dynasty resources once per session (value up to Profit Factor)."}}
{"_id": "rt_bg002", "name": "RT Background: Void-Born Mariner", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Common Lore (Rogue Traders), Navigate (Stellar), Operate (Voidship), Scholastic Lore (Astromancy), Tech-Use\n\nStarting Talents: Void Acclimatised, Technical Knock\n\nStarting Equipment: Void suit, personal vox, data-slate with star charts, toolkit, 3 doses de-tox\n\nBackground Bonus: Child of the Void: +20 Navigate (Stellar) and Operate (Voidship). Zero-gravity penalties reduced by 20.\n\nAptitudes: Intelligence or Fieldcraft\n\nBackground: Born between the stars, these mariners know the void better than any planet-dweller.", "benefit": "Aptitudes: Intelligence or Fieldcraft | Child of the Void: +20 Navigate (Stellar) and Operate (Voidship). Zero-gravity penalties reduced by 20."}}
{"_id": "rt_bg003", "name": "RT Background: Missionary", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Charm, Command, Common Lore (Imperial Creed), Forbidden Lore (Heresy), Linguistics (High Gothic)\n\nStarting Talents: Air of Authority, Peer (Ecclesiarchy)\n\nStarting Equipment: Devotional tome, missionary robes, laspistol, censer, 3 doses sacred unguents\n\nBackground Bonus: Fires of Faith: once per session, may re-roll a failed Willpower test for self or ally within voice range. +10 Command vs religious topics.\n\nAptitudes: Willpower or Social\n\nBackground: Carrying the light of the Emperor to the darkest corners of the galaxy.", "benefit": "Aptitudes: Willpower or Social | Fires of Faith: once per session, may re-roll a failed Willpower test for self or ally within voice range. +10 Command vs religious topics."}}
{"_id": "rt_bg004", "name": "RT Background: Explorator", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Common Lore (Adeptus Mechanicus), Forbidden Lore (Archaeotech), Scholastic Lore (any), Tech-Use, Trade (Technomat)\n\nStarting Talents: Mechadendrite Use (Utility), Technical Knock\n\nStarting Equipment: Mechadendrite (utility), combi-tool, data-slate, robes of the Machine God, 3 vials sacred unguents\n\nBackground Bonus: Blessed by the Omnissiah: Tech-Use tests to repair or identify archaeotech are Routine (+20) instead of their normal difficulty.\n\nAptitudes: Intelligence or Tech\n\nBackground: Servants of the Omnissiah seeking lost knowledge and ancient technology across the stars.", "benefit": "Aptitudes: Intelligence or Tech | Blessed by the Omnissiah: Tech-Use tests to repair or identify archaeotech are Routine (+20) instead of their normal difficulty."}}
{"_id": "rt_bg005", "name": "RT Background: Arch-Militant", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Athletics, Common Lore (War), Intimidate, Medicae, Weapon Training (any two)\n\nStarting Talents: Combat Master, Weapon Training (any additional)\n\nStarting Equipment: Best-quality weapon of choice, carapace armour, combat vest, 3 doses stimm, micro-bead\n\nBackground Bonus: Void Combat Veteran: +10 BS and WS aboard starships and in zero-gravity. Ignore zero-gravity movement penalties.\n\nAptitudes: Offence or Strength\n\nBackground: Soldiers of fortune who have seen war across a dozen star systems.", "benefit": "Aptitudes: Offence or Strength | Void Combat Veteran: +10 BS and WS aboard starships and in zero-gravity. Ignore zero-gravity movement penalties."}}
{"_id": "rt_bg006", "name": "RT Background: Navigator", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Common Lore (Navis Nobilite), Forbidden Lore (the Warp), Navigate (Warp), Psyniscience, Scholastic Lore (Astromancy)\n\nStarting Talents: Warp Sense, Resistance (Psychic Powers)\n\nStarting Equipment: Navigator robes, sealed warp eye headband, personal vox, star charts, data-slate\n\nBackground Bonus: Warp Eye: the Navigator's third eye may be used to emit a beam of warp energy. Once per encounter: 1d10+WPB Energy damage, Pen WPB, 15m range.\n\nAptitudes: Perception or Psyker\n\nBackground: Members of the ancient Navigator Houses, mutants who can guide ships through the Warp.", "benefit": "Aptitudes: Perception or Psyker | Warp Eye: the Navigator's third eye may be used to emit a beam of warp energy. Once per encounter: 1d10+WPB Energy damage, Pen WPB, 15m range."}}
{"_id": "rt_bg007", "name": "RT Background: Seneschal", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Charm, Commerce, Common Lore (Rogue Traders), Inquiry, Scrutiny\n\nStarting Talents: Peer (Underworld), Clues from the Crowds\n\nStarting Equipment: Fine clothing, personal vox, data-slate, 500 thrones in trade goods or currency, concealed autopistol\n\nBackground Bonus: Eye for Value: automatically know the approximate value of any mundane item. +20 Commerce tests for buying or selling.\n\nAptitudes: Fellowship or Knowledge\n\nBackground: The Rogue Trader's right hand \u2014 administrators, logisticians, and deal-makers without equal.", "benefit": "Aptitudes: Fellowship or Knowledge | Eye for Value: automatically know the approximate value of any mundane item. +20 Commerce tests for buying or selling."}}
{"_id": "rt_bg008", "name": "RT Background: Astropath Transcendent", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Starting Skills: Common Lore (Adeptus Astra Telepathica), Forbidden Lore (the Warp), Linguistics (any), Psyniscience\n\nStarting Talents: Warp Sense, Strong Minded\n\nStarting Equipment: Psy focus, light robes, micro-bead, personal vox\n\nBackground Bonus: Soul Binding: already soul-bound to the Emperor. Immune to the first failed Fear test against Warp entities each session. Starts as Psy Rating 1 Psyker.\n\nAptitudes: Willpower or Psyker\n\nBackground: Blind psychic communicators whose souls have been bound to the Emperor, allowing reliable astropathic communication across the void.", "benefit": "Aptitudes: Willpower or Psyker | Soul Binding: already soul-bound to the Emperor. Immune to the first failed Fear test against Warp entities each session. Starts as Psy Rating 1 Psyker."}}
{"_id": "rt_ro001", "name": "RT Role: Rogue Trader", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Commerce, Fellowship, Leadership, Offence, Social\n\nRole Talent: Air of Authority or Into the Jaws of Hell\n\nRole Bonus: Master of My Fate: once per session, declare any one test as automatically succeeding with DoS equal to Fellowship bonus.", "benefit": "Master of My Fate: once per session, declare any one test as automatically succeeding with DoS equal to Fellowship bonus."}}
{"_id": "rt_ro002", "name": "RT Role: Explorator", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Intelligence, Knowledge, Perception, Tech, Willpower\n\nRole Talent: Mechadendrite Use or Technical Knock\n\nRole Bonus: Quest for Knowledge: spend Fate to automatically succeed any Tech-Use or Lore test with DoS equal to Intelligence bonus.", "benefit": "Quest for Knowledge: spend Fate to automatically succeed any Tech-Use or Lore test with DoS equal to Intelligence bonus."}}
{"_id": "rt_ro003", "name": "RT Role: Missionary", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Fellowship, Leadership, Social, Willpower\n\nRole Talent: Air of Authority or Into the Jaws of Hell\n\nRole Bonus: Fires of Faith: spend Fate to grant all allies within 30m immunity to Fear and Pinning until end of next round.", "benefit": "Fires of Faith: spend Fate to grant all allies within 30m immunity to Fear and Pinning until end of next round."}}
{"_id": "rt_ro004", "name": "RT Role: Arch-Militant", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Ballistic Skill, Offence, Strength, Toughness, Weapon Skill\n\nRole Talent: Combat Master or Swift Attack\n\nRole Bonus: Combat Mastery: once per round, make one additional Standard Attack as a Free Action.", "benefit": "Combat Mastery: once per round, make one additional Standard Attack as a Free Action."}}
{"_id": "rt_ro005", "name": "RT Role: Navigator", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Intelligence, Perception, Psyker, Willpower\n\nRole Talent: Warp Sense or Psyniscience\n\nRole Bonus: Charting the Void: +20 to all Navigate (Warp) tests. May attempt to predict warp storms and anomalies.", "benefit": "Charting the Void: +20 to all Navigate (Warp) tests. May attempt to predict warp storms and anomalies."}}
{"_id": "rt_ro006", "name": "RT Role: Seneschal", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Fellowship, Intelligence, Knowledge, Social\n\nRole Talent: Clues from the Crowds or Peer (any)\n\nRole Bonus: On the Right Path: spend Fate to automatically locate any resource, contact, or information within reach of the ship's influence.", "benefit": "On the Right Path: spend Fate to automatically locate any resource, contact, or information within reach of the ship's influence."}}
{"_id": "rt_ro007", "name": "RT Role: Astropath", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Intelligence, Knowledge, Perception, Psyker, Willpower\n\nRole Talent: Warp Sense or Strong Minded\n\nRole Bonus: Voice of the Emperor: spend Fate to send or receive an astropathic message of any complexity with perfect clarity, regardless of interference.", "benefit": "Voice of the Emperor: spend Fate to send or receive an astropathic message of any complexity with perfect clarity, regardless of interference."}}
{"_id": "rt_ro008", "name": "RT Role: Void-Master", "type": "trait", "img": "icons/svg/item-bag.svg", "system": {"description": "Role Aptitudes: Agility, Fieldcraft, Intelligence, Tech\n\nRole Talent: Technical Knock or Operate (Voidship)\n\nRole Bonus: Ace of the Void: once per combat, reroll any failed Operate (Voidship) or Navigate test and take the better result.", "benefit": "Ace of the Void: once per combat, reroll any failed Operate (Voidship) or Navigate test and take the better result."}}
